-klimakalender-007.jpg",[],{"type":33,"tag":54,"props":65,"children":68},{"alt":66,"src":67},"Klimakalender innen","/images/klimakalender/221201-klimakalender-010.jpg",[],{"type":33,"tag":40,"props":70,"children":71},{},[72],{"type":44,"value":73},"my main job in creating the calendar was creating the design principles of the calendar and layouting the finished product. we only used open source typefaces and one single highlight color to keep costs as low as possible.",{"type":33,"tag":40,"props":75,"children":76},{},[77,79],{"type":44,"value":78},"the calendar was published by the ",{"type":33,"tag":34,"props":80,"children":84},{"link":81,"text":82,"external":83},"external","unrast verlag","https://unrast-verlag.de/",[],{"title":5,"searchDepth":17,"depth":17,"links":86},[],"content:projects:klimakalender.md","projects/klimakalender.md",1707751735112]